I would prefer to see the percentage made greater, or for them to make an ability where we can give an MA a nice charge of aggro on a fight.  It would certainly be a neat trick if a chanter on a fight in a raid would be capable of getting any melee the aggro.  Say if the MA fell and the SA was having a hard time getting aggro, the chanter could use the ability and switch aggro to the SA.  Right now the aggro buff isnt good enough to do that, maybe if they left the aggro at 30% when it first came out, but not after the nerf in January.  <br>
